%guide_10: Now you have 20 seconds to bet. The biggest bet will be displayed here.
%guide_11: Take the action you want.\n Call: Match the biggest bet.
%guide_12: Auto Call: Match the biggest bet automatically.
%guide_13: Raise to: Raise the bet. The amount raised is twice that of the ante by default.
%guide_14: Fold: Quit this round. You can't enter the battlefield and your stakes won't be returned.
%guide_15: All In: Put all of your gold in the pot.
%guide_16: Keep an eye on your bet. If you don't raise to the biggest bet when time's up, you'll be taken as Fold.
%guide_17: If your bet is the biggest for now, your billboard will light up with your bet.
%guide_18: Don't rush to raise the bet. Let's see what will happen next...
%guide_19: Next come spell cards. \nSpell cards can impact your starting hand and the entire battle with their powerful effects.
%guide_2: Play as a lord and compete with other 3 lords.
%guide_20: There are three spell cards at each round.\nYou can make a bet whenever a spell card is revealed.
%guide_21: Mouse over the spell card to read its details.\nThe spell card may imbue your starting hand with magic.
%guide_22: When all spell cards are revealed, there is a battle among forces of remaining lords.
%guide_23: These are your Lord Abilities. Each Ability can be cast only once during the whole game. Use them wisely.
%guide_24: Your forces won! You can take all the gold.\nThe next round starts right now.
%guide_25: Lucky you!\nYour two cards have the same value. \nThese Basic warriors will be upgraded to more powerful Elite ones.
%guide_26: This time let's go all in. If your total gold is the biggest bet, the gold more than the winner's bet will be returned even when you lose this round.
%guide_27: You have scared other players. You can take all the gold without fighting!
%guide_28: This is all you should know. Now, start off and beat them all!
%guide_3: This is Tanny and he can unleash Volcanic Fury to deal huge damage. Let's start your first game with him.
%guide_5: The thrilling and exciting game will start right now. Brave lords, fight for your glory.
%guide_6: At the start of each round, every lord has 2 cards and needs to ante up some gold.
%guide_7: Here is your starting hand. It determines the class and number of your forces at this round.
%guide_8: There are four classes which can interact with each other. Attacking suppressed classes can deal extra damage and reduce the damage received.
%guide_9: You can have up to 13 warriors for each class. You have 13 Swordsmen and 12 Archer this round. What a strong hand!
%guide_battle_tips:
WASD can control the camera movement.
You can feel the fierce fighting style of the legion at close range!
%guide_inquire: Itching to start your first game? Beginner's Guide can help you.
%loading_text: 拥有命运王冠的凯撒帝国之主，站在竞技场的最高处注视着攫取自己皇权的诸侯，面色冷如寒冰，无人知道他是否真的会坐以待毙......
